title: Pennsylvania family reunites with lost cat after multi-car crash in Minnesota
description: A Pennsylvania family said that they have been reunited with their their cat who went missing after a Minnesota car accident. The feline is now safe at home.

title: Pat Perez's wife takes shot at LIV Golf star on social media as divorce looms
description: Pat Perez's wife, Ashley, who filed for divorce in November from the LIV Golf star, took at shot at her soon-to-be-ex-husband on social media.

title: Striking Massachusetts teachers accused of hosting 'pub crawl,' as Newton schools remain closed
description: Teachers in a Massachusetts town remain on strike and plan to gather at different restaurants and bars while schools have been closed for over a week.
